phrases: I am not happy with this, Handa-kun.
I took off five whole days to come to this island,
but all I have gotten to do is look for your house,
then suffer a hangover after a bunch of strange old guys got me drunk.
We are fishin''cuz you said you wanted to make the most of yer last day here.
Do Not Know any sightseein' spots here.
This was my big chance to see you write calligraphy at close proximity!
I cannot believe we are outdoors!
Are even his vacation goals indoors?
I had to listen to his theories on calligraphy all night.
I started doing the art back in grade school!
I am very particular about my brush!
I did not get a wink of sleep.
What do we catch with this?
You do not just put bait on a hook?
I have never seen these before!
Wait, is this yer first time fishin'?!
Do not lump me in with those city boys.
Uh, that will not help catchin' horse mackerel.
There is bait on the hooks, too...
I did not come to teach city folk fishin'.
I am going up above, so good luck, Miwa.
I am a man of the sea.
Then, drop the line where you threw the bait.
When the end of the pole wiggles...
Gramma said it would be good fishin' today.
We will have fried horse mackerel for dinner!
It feels like I got one!
It is definitely a big one!
I am a genius at fishing as well as calligraphy!
It is stuck in the shoal.
Naru has obtained Slightly Longish Stick!
I stink, I cannot fish, I am hot...
But I just landed that huge catch.
I want to write calligraphy with you, Sensei!
You hate outdoor activities too, do not you?
Let us go back to your house!
You will just say I have gotten worse again.
Did you really tell him that?!
Cannot you see anything from any viewpoint besides your own?!
This is why you are in a slump!
It is because he was looking at your earlier calligraphy.
You have not gotten worse, Handa.
If you had, you would not have placed at all, much less second.
Kousuke was focused on your earlier work.
he got anxious about losing his model.
That is what I am saying.
Handa, have you seen Kousuke's calligraphy?
No, I do not look at that stuff.
His calligraphy looks just like yours.
And your calligraphy is just like your dad's.
You are both only faithful to the fundamentals.
But I got first place with that, so are not the fundamentals best?
Was that a subtle dig at my father?
is to break new ground without fear of failure!
Remain in memories, not record books!
Lose the battle, win the war!
Only One is better than Number One!
Wow, did you tie that, Hina?
You cannot catch anything with that!
That is the incarnation of failure!
Hey, do not laugh so much.
But, it is just so simple-minded!
I will let you off for today.
They are having fun down there...
Were they able to fish right?
In the end, they have just been talkin' calligraphy here, too.
All this about bein' bad or not.
Are not it enough for someone good at it to be good?
I guess when ya reach the top, there are not nowhere left to go.
Maybe I will not catch hisan-iwo today, either.
Guess it is really impossible'round here.
But the village chief was sayin' he saw someone catch one here.
Want To call it a day?
All right, it is my last cast, so I will give it a try.
They say, if ya say Ebisu while castin' yer line, you will catch a hisan-iwo.
Ebisu, as in one of the Seven Lucky Gods?
But they fish for snapper in open sea.
If you could catch them at places like this, then anyone could be a fisherman.
But, if he catches one, we will have snapper sashimi for dinner.
How can we leave this island without eating anything tasty?
You guys forgot that you are trying to fish with that hook, did not you?
All right, let us pack up.
I am going to clean up, so hold onto it.
You have not caught anything yet, right?
All right, let us help, too!
Hey, you are in the way!
Dummy, you cannot land such a big one by yourself.
You just want to steal my thunder, do not you?!
That sure was a big one!
The hook broke up in midair!
Well, we caught a bunch of horse mackerel, so that is fine.
We will fry them at my place.
Since I came to this island, there are times when I really want to write calligraphy.
These are the ones Sensei caught.
Today, to celebrate our visit to this island...
These fish have ink on them...
That is wreckage from breaking new ground.
I would rather eat snapper, but oh well.
You guys work hard and grow,
You always did have that side to you.
To Kawafuji-san, I am just a commodity.
Do you know what he meant by breakin' new ground?
I always did like yer calligraphy, Sensei,
Flight 635 to Fukuoka will begin boarding at 10:20.
You did not need to come see us off.
Passengers, please proceed to the boarding gate.
It is only about three hours to Tokyo.
Well, I can understand the reluctance to part,
but you did not need to make this much fuss...
It tastes great if ya heat it in a toaster oven.
It is written Happiki Kaminari (Eight Lightning Beasts) ,
These TV rocks are a rock revolution!
What did you really come here for?
Why are the locals here so hyper?
There is time before your departure,
so you should buy some souvenirs, Kawafuji-kun.
I appreciate all you did for me.
The village children normally only interact with local people,
so they enjoyed playing with people from the city.
There is a bunch of toys.
It is like Santa Claus's house.
Want To take one with you?
Say, which product is this island known for?
I cannot take that much home.
How about a cell phone strap?
Take back a bunch of Baramon-kun for your friends in Tokyo.
I do not have any friends, so I will just buy one for me.
I am going to buy this!
Do not you mean, make me buy it?
Do not invoke the next world at your age.
But I really want to give this to Kawafuji!
sure know what he really likes!
You bought a lot of souvenirs.
I bragged to my coworkers about coming to Gotou, so I had to keep up appearances.
Flight 635 to Fukuoka will now begin boarding.
Sorry I could not provide you any hospitality at all.
Please board at gate number one.
I already know you are insensitive.
Well, I was just glad to see you doing well.
I can give a good report to Handa-sensei.
Although he sent you away, he was still worried.
I thought you would keep playing the rebel and say something like, As if he would worry.
maybe Dad does not hate me after all.
You are only just realizing that now?
Strict is not the same as hateful.
From the outside, I would say he is pretty doting.
I knew he would get caught.
That is why you wanted to...
Was he hiding a knife in those glasses?
Kawafuji, I am embarrassed as your friend.
Although I did all those rude things,
I am truly happy to have met you.
This is not a school trip.
If we continue on the same path,
we are likely to meet again.
I am also happy to have met you.
Instead of being jealous of some guy I do not know,
I feel better after meeting you face to face.
Are they trying to kill me?
The metal detector's capture ability is tremendous!
I am kind of embarrassed, myself...
I forgot to give'them the souvenir Grampa sent with me!
She should not have anything metal on her.
And we only just met them.
You want to go to Tokyo too, Hiro-nii?
Not so much that I want to go to Tokyo...
But I was thinkin', the day'll come when we will be leavin' the island, too.
I am in my last year of high school,
so I oughta consider that reality.
Hey, I was having a serious scene!
There is room for us in there!
Bet you will be lonely with your friends gone.
I can look forward to seeing them again.
What was the souvenir from Naru?
So that is what set it off.
